\begin_layout Itemize
Primal and dual formulations:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
p^{*}=\inf_{w,\xi,b}\underbrace{\sup_{\alpha,\lambda\succeq0}L(w,b,\xi,\alpha,\lambda)}_{\text{primal objective }}\pause\ge\sup_{\alpha,\lambda\succeq0}\underbrace{\inf_{w,b,\xi}L(w,b,\xi,\alpha,\lambda)}_{\text{dual objective }g(\alpha,\lambda)}=d^{*}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Pause

\end_layout

